      "statements": [
        "ASSERT VALUES foo (id INT) VALUES (123);"
      ],
      "expectedException": {
        "type": "io.confluent.ksql.parser.exception.ParseFailedException",
        "message": "mismatched input 'ASSERT'"
      }
    }

If you submit a query with RUN SCRIPT the same will happen

